<span id="freeTextContainer15439805510956187588">How to run things and hopefully remain popular but not give a monkey&apos;s if they hate you. How to instil enough fear in people that they at least show respect to your face.<br/><br/>Plenty of good lessons here for a politician, but adaptable by anyone if you don&apos;t mind being thought evil by your nearest and dearest. And I don&apos;t.</span>
