  <span id="freeText4357144410531232520" style="display:none">Mandatory reading for Earthlings. Incredible insights on humanity, experience, perception, glory and honor, power and survival. <br /><br />Will re-read.<br /><br />“Where the willingness is great, the difficulties cannot be great.”<br /><br />"And in examining their life and deeds it will be seen that they owed nothing to fortune but the opportunity which gave them matter to be shaped into the form that they thought fit; and without that opportunity their powers would have been wasted, and without their powers the opportunity would have come in vain." <br /><br />- The Prince</span>
